OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening and night with a few
OL,7,Fscattered showers, one or two on the
OL,8,Fheavy side. Patchy mist and fog
OL,9,Fdeveloping around coasts through the
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud
OL,13,Fwith afternoon showers developing,
OL,14,Fsome of which will be heavy with a
OL,15,Frisk of thunder.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,18,FUnsettled and changeable through this
OL,19,Fperiod with showers or longer spells
OL,20,Fof rain. Often rather windy.
